"title": "4016: life, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4016",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Seen by Scripture as the climax of the work of creation, life is a gift of God and is to be treated with reverence and respect.</p>\n<h2>Life is from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:15\">ACT 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25\">ACT 17:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6\">1SA 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:13\">PSA 139:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:28\">ACT 17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:14–4:15</a></p>\n<h2>The ultimate duration of life is unknown to people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4\">PSA 39:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:2\">GEN 27:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:14\">JAS 4:13–4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Life is precious</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:31\">MAT 10:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">GEN 1:26–1:27</a> <em>Since all people are made in the image of God they are of value to him and should be so to each other</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5-Gen9:6\">GEN 9:5–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:7-Ps49:9\">PSA 49:7–49:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:14\">PSA 139:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a></p>\n<h2>God's presence in life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:16\">DEU 30:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:6\">PSA 23:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5-Ps71:6\">PSA 71:5–71:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:9\">PSA 71:9</a></p>\n<h2>Life is to be lived for God</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:13\">ECC 12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:23\">JER 10:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:39\">MAT 10:39</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:21\">PHP 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>The span of human life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:8-Eccl12:8\">ECC 11:8–12:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:10\">PSA 90:10</a></p>\n<h3>Life is temporary</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1\">2CO 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:12\">PSA 49:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:15-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:15–103:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:12\">ISA 38:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:13-2Pet1:14\">2PE 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Life is short</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:15\">1CH 29:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1\">JOB 14:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14\">JAS 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6-Job7:7\">JOB 7:6–7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:9\">JOB 8:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:25\">JOB 9:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:2\">JOB 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:6\">PSA 39:4–39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:47\">PSA 89:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:12\">PSA 90:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:11\">PSA 102:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:4\">PSA 144:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:12\">ECC 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">ISA 40:6–40:8</a></p>\n<h3>The termination of life by death is due to sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:22\">1CO 15:22</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of long life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:3-Gen5:32\">GEN 5:3–5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:29\">GEN 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:10-Gen11:32\">GEN 11:10–11:32</a></p>\n<h3>A full span of years</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:16\">PRO 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:25-Exod23:26\">EXO 23:25–23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:26\">JOB 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:2\">PRO 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:11\">PRO 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:27\">PRO 10:27</a></p>\n<h2>Attitudes to life</h2>\n<h3>Life loved</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:10\">1PE 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:12-Ps34:13\">PSA 34:12–34:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:21\">JOB 8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:16\">PSA 91:16</a></p>\n<h3>Life despised</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:22-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:22–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:16\">JOB 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:1\">JOB 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:17\">ECC 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:8\">JON 4:8</a></p>",
